// "Exactly N" ([CR#601.2c]) — a fixed cardinality. The single count goes in
// BOTH bounds of the underlying `Range`, so `Exactly(1)` ≡ `Range(Some 1,
// Some 1)`. The most common quantity by far (single targets / single choices).
(
    name: "Exactly",
    template: "exactly ${0}",
    kinds: [Quantity],
    params: [Count],
    body: Range(Param(0), Param(0)),
)
